arts.ttl: Richie Wellens on Leyton Orient's 2-1 loss at Lincoln City
arts.sum: “We dominated the first half, we’ve hit the crossbar, but the amount of areas we get into and we don’t get a shot, it’s happening too often. "Jovon looked like the only one for us in the first half and I’m pleased he’s got his goal.

arts.ttl: Cameron McGeehan gives Northampton victory over Leyton Orient
arts.sum: The second half goal proved decisive at Sixfields.
